            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大埔布心排村單位遇竊  失利是及葡萄酒",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"布心排村發生爆竊案。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4972f9c05b0ac0b69fed5d1378bd2e1d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250224/_2025022414130832157.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">布心排村發生爆竊案。楊偉亨攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（24日）晨11時許，大埔布心排村一名男戶主赫見屋內有搜掠痕跡，門戶被撬毀，於是報警，警方到場調查，該村屋高兩層，外有兩米高鐵皮圍欄，經點算後證實損失一批利是、紅酒及白酒，共值2000多元。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4100049/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男戶主（右）協助警方調查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a27e5ba135967b033d3bbe9e8915ef31/2025-02/01_0_15.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男戶主（右）協助警方調查。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4100050/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"男戶主（右）協助警方調查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0a7bb9c7bf74f03653204681f531e696/2025-02/02_1_38.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n     